Paste these values in a file called .p4config in home dir

export P4USER=<username>
export P4CLIENT=<machine-name>
export P4PORT=<P4 Service URL : Port>
export PKGGET_DEPOTS=<Mount points>
export P4DIFF=vimdiff

Use command "source .p4config" in terminal to set perforce

Create a perforce workspace directory by using a name such as "p4/perforce"

Move to that directory and issue command p4 client

Save the file and your perforce is configured
